    <item>
      <title>我不许可</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/%E6%88%91%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%B8%E5%8F%AF/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 21:20:00 &#43;0800</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/%E6%88%91%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%B8%E5%8F%AF/</guid>
      <description><p>如题，我不许可这样的表达作为“女性主义经典电影”和其它优秀的作品相提并论。我看的电影也并不多，表达不准确的地方烦请斧正。</p>
<p>首先，电影是需要真实的。它可以超现实，可以象征，可以夸张，可以有全新的世界观，但说到底，电影仍然要回归生活，回归真实的人，回到那些最细腻、也最有说服力的情感、处境和审美经验中去。</p></description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>What to do when waiting for agents working</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/what-to-do-when-waiting-for-agents/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 23:26:00 &#43;0800</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/what-to-do-when-waiting-for-agents/</guid>
      <description><h2 id="organize-project-folders">Organize Project Folders</h2>
<p>Review the revisions made in previous tasks, reorganize the project folders, refine the README, and try to write out a clear map down.</p>
<p>Manage to keep the agent’s modifications within the bounds of <strong>my own intentions and judgment</strong>, or we easily lose control.</p>
<h2 id="review-concepts-and-theorems-used-in-my-courses">Review Concepts and Theorems used in my courses.</h2>
<p>Concepts in math are tightly woven together: stochastic processes sit at the heart of time series analysis, which also demands a strong command of statistics; real analysis provides much of the rigor needed to make sense of results in stochastic analysis;  not to mention how algebra quietly but powerfully runs through nearly every path in mathematics, statistics, and computer science.</p></description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Joel Mokyr 讲座大纲</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/joel-mokyr-summary/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 02:01:23 &#43;0800</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/joel-mokyr-summary/</guid>
      <description><h1 id="joel-mokyr-讲座大纲">Joel Mokyr 讲座大纲</h1>
<p>ai简单整理。</p>
<h2 id="主旨">主旨</h2>
<p>这场讲座并非只是泛泛空谈“思想自由很重要”、“创新驱动发展”等口号，而是通过梳理历史上“思想市场”的发展来告诉我们：一个社会是否能形成高质量的 market for ideas，决定了它能不能持续生产、筛选、信任并应用 useful knowledge，进而影响文化演化、技术创新与长期经济增长。</p></description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>The art of &#39;at most&#39;</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/art-of-at-most/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Jan 2026 12:00:00 &#43;0800</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/art-of-at-most/</guid>
      <description><h1 id="the-art-of-at-most">The art of &lsquo;at most&rsquo;</h1>
<p>As we all know, to calculate &rsquo;exactly&rsquo; is notoriously difficult. Why? For example, when we write an assignment on paper, a minimum word‑count line is often printed so that readers do not need to count every word to know whether the requirement is met; a single glance tells them whether the text reaches at least that line and gives an approximate conclusion that it passes.</p></description>
    </item>
    
